01:23:33.376 --> 01:23:37.077
- [Watts] All right,
I'll see you there.

01:23:37.079 --> 01:23:39.646
(electronic beeping)

01:23:39.648 --> 01:23:42.783
(car engine running)

01:23:47.757 --> 01:23:49.390
(gentle instrumental music)

01:23:49.392 --> 01:23:52.259
(paper rustling)

01:24:06.809 --> 01:24:09.476
(bag zipping)

01:24:19.055 --> 01:24:21.822
(electronic beeping)

01:24:21.824 --> 01:24:24.625
(phone ringing)

01:24:30.433 --> 01:24:31.832
- [Woman] Markus?

01:24:31.834 --> 01:24:33.634
- [Markus] Yeah, look,

01:24:33.636 --> 01:24:35.769
I'm gonna be leaving
town for a while.

01:24:37.273 --> 01:24:39.273
I can't talk a lot
about it right now.

01:24:40.676 --> 01:24:42.376
I'll talk to you in a few days.

01:24:51.720 --> 01:24:55.456
(upbeat instrumental music)

01:25:17.513 --> 01:25:20.347
(metal thudding)

01:25:44.607 --> 01:25:47.774
(car engine running)

01:26:51.440 --> 01:26:53.440
(electronic beeping)

01:26:53.442 --> 01:26:55.342
- [Frank] Hey, asshole,
answer your phone.

01:26:55.344 --> 01:26:58.212
I think I have something
you might want,

01:26:58.214 --> 01:26:59.279
your girl, Staci.

01:27:00.549 --> 01:27:03.517
Oh, and I picked up some
of my money from your boy.

01:27:03.519 --> 01:27:04.451
Oh, don't worry.

01:27:04.453 --> 01:27:05.819
You won't find much left of him.

01:27:06.922 --> 01:27:09.556
Give me a call as
soon as possible.

01:27:09.558 --> 01:27:10.524
You have something of mine,

01:27:10.526 --> 01:27:12.359
and I have something of yours.

01:27:12.361 --> 01:27:13.994
Call me so we can negotiate.

01:27:13.996 --> 01:27:15.362
Bye.

01:27:15.364 --> 01:27:17.698
(car engine running)

01:27:17.700 --> 01:27:20.500
(phone ringing)

01:27:30.980 --> 01:27:32.246
Thanks for calling me back.

01:27:32.248 --> 01:27:33.914
Glad you listened to my message.

01:27:33.916 --> 01:27:35.782
We need to meet up, Markus,

01:27:35.784 --> 01:27:37.317
sort all this out.

01:27:37.319 --> 01:27:38.285
Where's my money?

01:27:39.288 --> 01:27:40.254
- A safe place.

01:27:41.390 --> 01:27:42.956
- [Frank] Staci's
right here, man.

01:27:42.958 --> 01:27:44.258
She's fine and in good health,

01:27:44.260 --> 01:27:45.959
and I wanna keep it that way,

01:27:45.961 --> 01:27:47.628
as long as you do what I say.

01:27:48.931 --> 01:27:50.998
- [Staci] Markus, are you there?

01:27:52.968 --> 01:27:53.900
- Things will be fine

01:27:53.902 --> 01:27:55.569
as long as you cooperate.

01:27:55.571 --> 01:27:57.971
I say we settle this
once and for all.

01:27:57.973 --> 01:28:00.707
I don't want things
to get out of hand.

01:28:00.709 --> 01:28:03.277
Meet me at Twins in
and hour and a half.

01:28:03.279 --> 01:28:04.978
You be there with my money,

01:28:04.980 --> 01:28:06.813
I release the girl.

01:28:08.050 --> 01:28:09.383
See you then.

01:28:10.819 --> 01:28:13.387
(dramatic instrumental music)

01:28:13.389 --> 01:28:16.523
(car engine running)

01:28:50.793 --> 01:28:53.527
(electronic beeping)

01:28:53.529 --> 01:28:55.762
(metal thudding)

01:28:55.764 --> 01:28:57.764
(gentle instrumental music)

01:28:57.766 --> 01:29:00.767
(metal clattering)

01:29:26.795 --> 01:29:29.663
(metal thudding)

01:29:45.614 --> 01:29:47.147
I just delivered a message.

01:29:48.550 --> 01:29:50.550
They're releasing Staci
on Anderson and Boyd

01:29:50.552 --> 01:29:52.052
by the Fourth Street Bridge.

01:29:53.555 --> 01:29:55.422
I never said she'd
be here with me.

01:30:00.162 --> 01:30:01.628
Now hand over the money.

01:30:06.935 --> 01:30:09.669
(bag thudding)

01:30:14.743 --> 01:30:15.675
(metal scraping)

01:30:15.677 --> 01:30:17.878
(yelling)

01:30:28.157 --> 01:30:31.057
(metal thudding)

01:30:59.588 --> 01:31:01.855
(grunting)

01:31:03.459 --> 01:31:07.060
(gentle instrumental music)

01:33:47.889 --> 01:33:51.691
(upbeat instrumental music)
